}, {"cid": 1465079, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2581, "w": 1936}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1618555954, "type": "image", "url": "ww/ww32qyd7xhq6a7psmfixevor3eafsf6g.jpeg"}, {"cid": 1465159, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2581, "w": 1936}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1618556795, "type": "image", "url": "yf/yfkdeowszmu7dit4lh5ov7zcsqk5rrlt.jpeg"}, {"cid": 1465209, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1/2R（F-f）=Fr-fR\nfR=F（2r-R）\nf=F(2r-R)/R\n我继续算是这样，但是这样f可能小于零（反向）啊(>﹏<)", "timestamp": 1618557362, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465237, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "反向也很正常啊😂 你可以想象实际情况 都是有可能的 和角度也有关系", "timestamp": 1618557608, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有点难以想象我拖着圆柱往前走摩擦力还帮我推着走，\n发出了以上学渣发言(>ω<)", "timestamp": 1618557727, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465261, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 也可以想象是摩擦力阻止转的太快 这样就好理解了", "timestamp": 1618557810, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1465289, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢(^o^）", "timestamp": 1618558045, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1479164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不应该是Fr+fR=(1/2)mR^2β吗……因为F-f=ma表明f的正方向是向后的，那力矩不是和F同向？", "timestamp": 1618746892, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1479248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 287347, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 应该是(1/2)R(F-f)=Fr+fR，得到3Rf=(R-2r)F从而f=F(R-2r)/(3R)吧，虽然还是会为负。采用另一种计算方式验算：参考点取在地上，考虑角动量变化率=力矩，有F(R+r)=(1/2)mR^2β+R*ma=(3/2)mR^2β，β=(F/m)(2/3)(R+r)/R^2，a=(F/m)(2/3)(1+r/R)，f=F-ma=(1/3)F-(2/3)(r/R)F=F(R-2r)/(3R)", "timestamp": 1618747554, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 287347, "reply": 18, "tag": null, "text": "有谁有lgq大物早上考试题的答案吗？那个圆柱在平面上滚动的摩擦力f到底是多少啊？", "timestamp": 1618554726, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618747555, "url": "", "vote": {}}}